{"tid":611532,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解簽名就等於有法律效力？","createTime":"2018-03-31T06:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T09:38:18.000Z","uid":4662,"like":19,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcf3ae377f28c51469b6823e5a9c01814ff1c5c","tid":611532,"uid":4662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:09:46.000Z","msg":"我求其亂簽一個名，有咩證據證明份野係我簽？"},{"pid":"39a2d491980d7d1a2d7e9f30848f9c12e7431467","tid":611532,"uid":4662,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ecc2bf4061a5eecdd08355b5007cbcd36a7877","tid":611532,"uid":68653,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"法律上 只要你簽既時候 係唔情願 被逼 <br />\n或者有隱藏條款（誤導成份）好似就可以無效<br />\n<br />\n利申 非法律狗 只係讀過crime<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0725ea26b63107d1044a42e9a69ac0d4dcdaf08f","tid":611532,"uid":4662,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c3ecc2bf4061a5eecdd08355b5007cbcd36a7877","tid":611532,"uid":68653,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"法律上 只要你簽既時候 係唔情願 被逼 <br />\n或者有隱藏條款（誤導成份）好似就可以無效<br />\n<br />\n利申 非法律狗 只係讀過crime<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:22:53.000Z","msg":"咁點證明係我簽？"},{"pid":"74de0fc2d43efaccce607006228cc7215e3dff59","tid":611532,"uid":29914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:26:59.000Z","msg":"睇下你簽既時侯，有無第三者在場囉，有既對方咪可以做證，證明份野係你簽。但如果無人做證。大部分情況都係舉證失敗，咪證明唔到份野係你簽囉。<br />\n<br />\n最好有咩問返律師意見啦。"},{"pid":"cca08795f88afe4316308dbe5285f6ff9d7ead11","tid":611532,"uid":4662,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74de0fc2d43efaccce607006228cc7215e3dff59","tid":611532,"uid":29914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:26:59.000Z","msg":"睇下你簽既時侯，有無第三者在場囉，有既對方咪可以做證，證明份野係你簽。但如果無人做證。大部分情況都係舉證失敗，咪證明唔到份野係你簽囉。<br />\n<br />\n最好有咩問返律師意見啦。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:28:51.000Z","msg":"咁就算有第三者係度，都可以係夾口供咁屈我。"},{"pid":"60e2155542f2d97e098b6b97340fa66063b2d6fd","tid":611532,"uid":99816,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:30:40.000Z","msg":"簽名只係作為證據 去attempt to prove your consent<br />\n並唔係最後結果，最後結果要等官判，睇晒所有呈堂證供<br />\n簽名本身如果係under Duress (e.g. 十鳩幾個人圍住你逼你簽) 咁就唔洗講係無效<br />\n<br />\n個key word 係 Consent /intention to create legally binding relationship<br />\n只要prove到有，唔理你係咪簽名，口號答應都可以計"},{"pid":"a8f0704fa1dfae54f5e2562e4feb84173afde683","tid":611532,"uid":99816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:32:26.000Z","msg":"證明你簽，一般都係筆跡對比，或其他環境證供/在場證人<br />\n所以你去律師樓簽買賣樓既協議，律師就係簽名既證人<br />\n簽遺囑，有d要有第三者見證"},{"pid":"7c7af321fc4b87c658e76dcb542919c46c0f3a5b","tid":611532,"uid":29914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cca08795f88afe4316308dbe5285f6ff9d7ead11","tid":611532,"uid":4662,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74de0fc2d43efaccce607006228cc7215e3dff59","tid":611532,"uid":29914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:26:59.000Z","msg":"睇下你簽既時侯，有無第三者在場囉，有既對方咪可以做證，證明份野係你簽。但如果無人做證。大部分情況都係舉證失敗，咪證明唔到份野係你簽囉。<br />\n<br />\n最好有咩問返律師意見啦。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:28:51.000Z","msg":"咁就算有第三者係度，都可以係夾口供咁屈我。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:32:38.000Z","msg":"你咁諗無錯。 但一般證人在庭宣誓或誓章都均有法律效力，發假誓都幾嚴重。我諗一般人唔會咁冒險咁做。"},{"pid":"dd889492cae5335c40c96d8d4644f8ed6c442e45","tid":611532,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c7af321fc4b87c658e76dcb542919c46c0f3a5b","tid":611532,"uid":29914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cca08795f88afe4316308dbe5285f6ff9d7ead11","tid":611532,"uid":4662,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74de0fc2d43efaccce607006228cc7215e3dff59","tid":611532,"uid":29914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:26:59.000Z","msg":"睇下